
## **.gitignore**

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.so
.Python
venv/
env/
ENV/
.venv
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt
.pytest_cache/
.coverage

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
.DS_Store

# Logs
*.log

# Data files (keep folder structure)
data/*.txt
!data/.gitkeep

# OS
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
